<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="no"><head><title>Forskrift om endringer i forskrift om truck og truckkjøring.</title><base href="https://lovdata.no/" /></head><body><header class="documentHeader" id="hode"><dl class="data-document-key-info"><dt class="xmlGenerated">XML generert</dt><dd class="xmlGenerated">2025-11-18 09:18:23</dd><dt class="legacyID">Datokode</dt><dd class="legacyID">FOR-1984-11-09-2016</dd><dt class="dokid">DokumentID</dt><dd class="dokid">LTI/forskrift/1984-11-09-2016</dd><dt class="ministry">Departement</dt><dd class="ministry"><ul><li>Kommunal- og arbeidsdepartementet</li></ul></dd><dt class="publishedIn">Publisert i</dt><dd class="publishedIn">Avd I 1984 Nr. 26</dd><dt class="dateInForce">I kraft fra</dt><dd class="dateInForce">1985-02-09</dd><dt class="changesToDocuments">Endrer</dt><dd class="changesToDocuments"><ul><li>forskrift/1974-04-18-9087</li></ul></dd><dt class="appliesTo">Gjelder for</dt><dd class="appliesTo">Norge</dd><dt class="basedOn">Hjemmel</dt><dd class="basedOn"><ul><li>lov/1977-02-04-4/§9</li><li>lov/1977-02-04-4/§17</li></ul></dd><dt class="dateOfPublication">Kunngjort</dt><dd class="dateOfPublication">1985-01-09</dd><dt class="title">Tittel</dt><dd class="title">Forskrift om endringer i forskrift om truck og truckkjøring.</dd><dt class="refid">RefID</dt><dd class="refid">forskrift/1984-11-09-2016</dd><dt class="table-of-contents">Innhold</dt><dd class="table-of-contents"><ul class="tocTopUl"><li>Forskrift om endringer i forskrift om truck og truckkjøring.</li></ul></dd></dl></header><main class="documentBody" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1984-11-09-2016" id="dokument"><h1>Forskrift om endringer i forskrift om truck og truckkjøring.</h1><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/" id="ledd-1">Direktoratet for arbeidstilsynet har 9. november 1984 med hjemmel i lov av 4. februar 1977 nr. 4 om arbeidervern og arbeidsmiljø § 9 og § 17 fastsatt følgende endringer i forskrift av 18. april 1974 om truck og truckkjøring.</article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">Forskriftens punkt 2.1 b skal lyde:</article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/" id="ledd-2">Løfteevne (største tillatte last) i kilo med maksimum løftehøyde og med tyngdepunktsavstand på:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1">400 mm for kapasitet mindre enn 1000 kg</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1">500 mm for kapasitet f.o.m. 1000 kg inntil 5000 kg</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/3/" id="ledd-2-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1">600 mm for kapasitet f.o.m. 5000 kg inntil 10000 kg.</article></article></li></ul></article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">Forskriftens punkt 2.2 skal lyde:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/4/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-4-ledd-1">fabrikantens navn</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/5/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-5-ledd-1">typebetegnelse</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/6/" id="ledd-2-punkt-6"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/6/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-6-ledd-1">fabrikasjons- eller serienummer</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/7/" id="ledd-2-punkt-7"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/7/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-7-ledd-1">tilleggsutstyrets vekt i kg</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1">tilleggsutstyrets største løfteevne med tyngepunktsavstand på:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">400 mm for kapasitet mindre enn 1000 kg</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">500 mm for kapasitet f.o.m. 1000 kg inntil 5000 kg</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="-" data-name="-"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">-</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/punkt/8/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="ledd-2-punkt-8-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">600 mm for kapasitet f.o.m. 5000 kg inntil 10000 kg.</article></article></li></ul></article></article></li></ul></article></main></body></html>